<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>römisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> künig,
                            <add>und auch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Speir</add>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des czolls
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> von Wirczburg von <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>czuhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und cze<expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> maint
                        wider <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> brief und freyheite.
                                <expan>Bit<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., daz ir uns gen
                                <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> künig, ewr
                            <add>gunstig</add> furdrüng
                            <add><expan>gnedigkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan></add> beweisen wöllet, daz
                        uns von seinen <expan>kuniglich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> ein brief werde und auch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Wirczbg</expan>
                        v<ex>er</ex>schreib, daz wir des czolls <expan>überhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und damit unbeswert <add>werden</add>, als wir des begnadet und gefreyet
                            <add>sein</add>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
